## Target Files

- `launcher.yaml`: runtime and entrypoint for local notify integration
- `targets/codex-runtime/package.yaml`: authored Codex runtime metadata
- `targets/codex-runtime/config.extra.toml`: optional passthrough for supported repo-local Codex config fields beyond managed `model` and `notify`
- `.codex/config.toml`: rendered managed Codex config
- `fixtures/codex-runtime/Notify.json`: pre-generated stable Codex notify smoke payload owned by this project
- `goldens/codex-runtime/*`: pre-generated stable stdout/stderr/exit contract owned by this project

Keep stdout reserved for Codex responses and write diagnostics to stderr only.
